def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace("O", "OO")

print(insert_after_character("Hello World!"))
print(insert_after_character("O"))
print(insert_after_character("Aardvark"))
print(insert_after_character("BOO"))
print(insert_after_character("ooO"))
```

```
HellO WOrld!
OO
Aardvark
